.container.section-anchor#whatisseek
  h1.text-center.well
    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-search
    | &nbsp;What is SEEK?
  .row
    .col-md-1
    .col-md-5.col-sm-6
      p.text-left
        | SEEK is an annual competition hosted by Robotics for Space Exploration (RSX). Competitors are given a task,
        | some robotic components to design and build a robot that can complete a series of challenges. SEEK was first held
        | in 2015 as a way of getting more people interested and active in robotics. We'd have to say we've been pretty successful!
